%%{init: {'theme':'base','themeVariables':{'fontFamily':'Calibri','fontSize':'18px'}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant SS as Sales Service
    participant MQ as Message Queue
    participant IS as Integration Service
    participant DB as DB (subscriptions)
    participant Q as Webhook Queue
    participant W as Webhook Worker
    participant TENANT as Tenant Endpoint

    SS->>SS: createInvoice() success
    SS->>MQ: emit "invoice.created"<br/>{ tenantId, invoiceId, ... }
    MQ->>IS: deliver event
    IS->>DB: lookup webhook subscriptions<br/>WHERE tenantId AND event LIKE 'invoice.*'
    DB-->>IS: [{ url, secret, event }]
    IS->>Q: push job per subscription
    Q->>W: pull job
    W->>W: build payload
    W->>W: sign HMAC-SHA256(secret, body)
    W->>TENANT: POST <url><br/>X-Reborn-Signature: <hmac><br/>X-Reborn-Event: invoice.created<br/>X-Reborn-Delivery: <uuid>
    alt 2xx response
      TENANT-->>W: 200 OK
      W->>DB: mark delivered
    else non-2xx
      TENANT-->>W: 5xx / timeout
      W->>Q: schedule retry (1m, 5m, 30m, 2h, 12h)
      Note over W,Q: After 5 fails → DLQ + alert admin
    end
